接口 KenBurnsView.TransitionListener

  • 封闭类:
    KenBurnsView

    public static interface KenBurnsView.TransitionListener
    A transition listener receives notifications when a transition starts or ends.

    • 方法概要

      方法 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      void onTransitionEnd(Transition transition)
      Notifies the end of a transition.
      void onTransitionStart(Transition transition)
      Notifies the start of a transition.

    • 方法详细资料

      • onTransitionStart

      • onTransitionEnd

        void onTransitionEnd(Transition transition)
        Notifies the end of a transition.
